OL,3,CClean Air Zone charges could increase
OL,4,Cas council faces #52m funding gap
OL,6,FDrivers could be charged more to enter
OL,7,FBristol's Clean Air Zone (CAZ) under
OL,8,Fcouncil plans that would also see
OL,9,Fdisabled badge holders pay for parking.
OL,11,FThe current #9 daily fee has not been
OL,12,Fincreased since the scheme launched in
OL,13,F2022, and council officers are seeking
OL,14,Fapproval to ask the government for
OL,15,Fpermission to raise it in line with
OL,16,Finflation.
