OL,3,CClean Air Zone charges could increase
OL,4,Cas council faces #52m funding gap
OL,6,FBudget papers to be considered by
OL,7,Fcouncillors on 15 January, show it
OL,8,Fwould bring in an extra #200,000 each
OL,9,Fyear in 2026/27 and 2027/28. It's
OL,10,Funderstood the council would not make
OL,11,Fany money as income from the charge
OL,12,Fwill decrease as more vehicles become
OL,13,FCAZ compliant.
OL,15,FOther budget proposals affecting
OL,16,Fdrivers include introducing charges
OL,17,Ffor disabled parking bays, bringing in
OL,18,F#100,000 a year; and pay-and-display
OL,19,Ffor the Downs, which is expected to
OL,20,Freap #200,000.
