OL,3,CClean Air Zone charges could increase
OL,4,Cas council faces #52m funding gap
OL,6,FMore traffic wardens would be
OL,7,Frecruited over the next 24 months to
OL,8,Fenforce bus-lanes so the council can
OL,9,F"meet its sustainable transport
OL,10,Fgoals", earning the authority a net
OL,11,F#100,000 per year.
OL,13,FPlans previously agreed to install
OL,14,Fautomatic number plate recognition
OL,15,Fcameras at "Keep Clear" zigzag
OL,16,Fmarkings outside schools, which would
OL,17,Fraise #50,000. While an increase in
OL,18,Fcar parking charges in 2026/27 at a
OL,19,Fstandard fixed price per hour is
OL,20,Fexpected to bring in a further
OL,21,F#500,000.
