OL,6,FBristol City Council's cross-party
OL,7,Ffinance sub-committee will consider a
OL,8,Fraft of money-saving and cash-raising
OL,9,Fproposals on 15 and 16 January.
OL,11,FUnder the new committee system, the
OL,12,Fprocess is different for the first
OL,13,Ftime since the mayoral model was
OL,14,Fabolished in 2024.
OL,16,FPreviously, the budget was rubber-
OL,17,Fstamped at cabinet before going to a
OL,18,Fvote at full council.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
