OL,6,FA report to next week's meetings said
OL,7,FWestminster's local government
OL,8,Fsettlement announced on 18 December
OL,9,Fwas better than expected but still
OL,10,Fleft a massive funding blackhole of
OL,11,F#42million in 2025/26.
OL,13,FIn a blog post on the authority's
OL,14,Fwebsite, council leader Cllr Tony Dyer
OL,15,Fsaid: "Across the country, councils of
OL,16,Fall shapes and sizes face bankruptcy.
OL,18,F"Bristol is no exception and will face
OL,19,Fbankruptcy if we can't close a
OL,20,F#52million funding gap over the next
OL,21,Ffive years.
OL,26,@wD@GOUzD@AOU
