OL,6,F"This needs to start straight away.
OL,7,FThere is no doubt that it means
OL,8,Fdifficult choices, more taxes and
OL,9,Fcharges, and we recognise that the
OL,10,Fmoney we raise does not go as far as
OL,11,Fit once did.
OL,13,F"We don't like that any more than
OL,14,Flocal taxpayers do, but it is the
OL,15,Freality we must contend with.
OL,17,F"We need to take a bigger, bolder, and
OL,18,Fmore politically courageous approach
OL,19,Fto our budget.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
