OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F435A1736439352
OL,3,CClean Air Zone charges could increase
OL,4,Cas council faces #52m funding gap
OL,6,F"We cannot keep salami-slicing public
OL,7,Fservices, nor can we pretend that
OL,8,Fwords like 'efficiency' and
OL,9,F'productivity' hold all the answers.
OL,11,F"These approaches have been tried
OL,12,Fbefore.
OL,14,F"Too often the savings haven't been
OL,15,Fmade, the can has been kicked down the
OL,16,Froad, and we have overspent our budget.
OL,18,F"This is a very tough time for
OL,19,FBristol, and we recognise the
OL,20,Fdifficulties being faced by many
OL,21,Fhouseholds and communities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
