OL,6,F"We will keep fighting your corner `
OL,7,Fseeking fair, longer-term funding from
OL,8,Fgovernment and working with partners
OL,9,Flike the NHS and regional combined
OL,10,Fauthority to provide more fairly
OL,11,Ffunded, joined-up services.
OL,13,F"This will not be a perfect or
OL,14,Fpainless process ` with the challenges
OL,15,Fwe face it was never going to be."
